The tentative agreement calls for <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">3M</ENAMEX> to use the <ENAMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">115,000 - square - foot</ENAMEX> plant and <ENAMEX TYPE="QUANTITY">19 acres</ENAMEX> of land for research laboratories .
<ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">Control Data</ENAMEX> has been seeking a buyer for the facility since it folded its <ENAMEX TYPE="ORG">ETA Systems Inc.</ENAMEX> supercomputer unit <ENAMEX TYPE="DATE">this past April</ENAMEX> .
